{"tid":784551,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[物理撚入嚟解答下文科撚］戶外運動應該著深色定淺色衫？","createTime":"2018-08-18T13:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T10:06:22.000Z","uid":167330,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"caa9a9fe0abe931776551a67b24564d6f52128f6","tid":784551,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:02:42.000Z","msg":"話說喺早排陽光猛烈嘅日子小弟著咗套全黑嘅運動衫褲踩單車，但就俾班friend笑鳩我著深色衫吸熱（佢地都係著淺色衫）。<br />\n<br />\n小弟我得中三嘅物理程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係知黑色係良好嘅輻射吸收體，雖然吸熱勁咗，但理論上散熱都快咗，既然身體溫度高過戶外溫度，咁散熱效能應該高啲？<br />\n<br />\n而我班friend就認為淺色衫可以反射返啲陽光同輻射，令到身體冇咁熱。<br />\n<br />\n咁我諗呢條問題應該涉及究竟散熱同吸熱邊樣快啲，但奈何我唔識物理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁假設喺室外氣溫係33&deg;c ，人體氣溫38&deg;c，並且喺陽光直接照射下運動，究竟運動嗰陣應該著淺色定深色衫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能條問題對你地嚟講好戇鳩，但我未學過真係唔識，屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661236da1e4e6d0591b4237aca0947015544fe92","tid":784551,"uid":132587,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:04:48.000Z","msg":"讀緊小一有中三物理程度咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a40702e99ce47f1bf8f413ffd82dd3972e819d","tid":784551,"uid":167330,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"661236da1e4e6d0591b4237aca0947015544fe92","tid":784551,"uid":132587,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:04:48.000Z","msg":"讀緊小一有中三物理程度咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:06:12.000Z","msg":"吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我有邊到講錯野咩？"},{"pid":"0544202e1c2cabd9805efb3382116415e5b3d37d","tid":784551,"uid":112583,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:07:06.000Z","msg":"仆你個街<br />\n<br />\n人體氣溫38度叫發燒<br />\n<br />\n好快啲睇醫生"},{"pid":"bd51090264617b6e0237e1443