Z","msg":"個main point 係日曬時紅外線多<br />\n<br />\n即係陽光猛既時候有net absorption<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea0527b47887a23f53862365451ce83f052a753e","tid":784551,"uid":34771,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:11:15.000Z","msg":"人體主要靠排汗散熱<br />\n<br />\n黑色散熱快關人體撚事"},{"pid":"49a543184a161d58235102194887c70eb0656ef1","tid":784551,"uid":199675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:12:35.000Z","msg":"依條問題都困擾咗我好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我理解係: 人體係net absorber (absorb &gt; emit) 所以要穿著淺色衫 以減慢吸熱的速率<br />\n<br />\n而於點解人體係net absorber 就去搵搵你中學嘅物理老師啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3fa4cc53c6648f31f4c97e06ba4d8c1bdbb0d30","tid":784551,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bf27b8fbfac253666e68541ca33382d96d00340","tid":784551,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dec007682bbf97f42374cb1d699c2050ad044d7e","tid":784551,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:09:22.000Z","msg":"淺色高反光，奶左野易搵你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:10:52.000Z","msg":"認真好奇想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:13:17.000Z","msg":"講真"},{"pid":"fa15ebaeba317fb5e05c7d60e5efd3ce941b0508","tid":784551,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 著黑衫太陽光輻射升溫仲快過熱空氣傳導比你，睇下唔過一個鐘就曬黑就知。人體散熱係靠汗蒸發的。"},{"pid":"fbbe6b780d7706c147e7936dfa9e76126871dba6","tid":784551,"uid":12517,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"661236da1e4e6d0591b4237aca0947015544fe92","tid":784551,"uid":132587,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:04:48.000Z","msg":"讀緊小一有中三物理程度咁勁<img src=\"