ces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？即係一樣？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:42:25.000Z","msg":"淺色會涼啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508a01c4065971cc86c1edf3dede13db6c489564","tid":784551,"uid":35598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:44:10.000Z","msg":"你個人38度唔代表件衫係38度呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺件吸到熱辣辣嘅黑衫喺身咪熱死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf344ec3c6040e3c6d28e0d05e63ec9139eda8c1","tid":784551,"uid":191864,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T14:21:18.000Z","msg":"人體體表溫度廿度左右<br />\n37係體內核心恆溫既溫度..."},{"pid":"dff3d6c33f8ed7463599770ea23dabd5356c1ead","tid":784551,"uid":161304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T14:32:47.000Z","msg":"熱分傳導，幅射，倒流三分面傳播<br />\n深色衫會吸收多咗空外既紫外線而熱左<br />\n「幅射」<br />\n利申：中學physics<br />\n<br />\nBtw 樓主你心跳而家點"},{"pid":"dc041c04fa0067814fa3fc4f152c57f685b6d7cb","tid":784551,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dff3d6c33f8ed7463599770ea23dabd5356c1ead","tid":784551,"uid":161304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T14:32:47.000Z","msg":"熱分傳導，幅射，倒流三分面傳播<br />\n深色衫會吸收多咗空外既紫外線而熱左<br />\n「幅射」<br />\n利申：中學physics<br />\n<br />\nBtw 樓主你心跳而家點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T14:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲記得我心有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上個星期心口痛同高壓有啲高又入過院，前日先出院。而家等緊排期做手術。"},{"pid":"f1a76af5e794163dd5816f2dc0326f70a684ba5b","tid":784551,"uid":36417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:05:27.000Z","msg":"認真答你<br />\n要睇個heat source 係邊個 <br />\n出邊做運動太陽光就係heat source, 而唔係自己。因為人唔係用radiation 排熱 係用排汗，所以你要做既就係防止吸熱 著返件白色衫<br />\n<br />\n冬天著深色係因為外凍過內 你自己變左heat source, 你要保熱就著深色"},{"pid":"7ae3a4fc5c5ac3eee830138e5fa593270cab71c6","tid":784551,"uid":4586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:22:03.000Z","msg":"On9問題 本黎唔想認真答<br />\nLet absord=x      Release=y<br />\nX&gt;y 因為太陽俾你嘅能量一定快過你散<br />\n係同時進行情況下 兩個都乘一個rate=r which假設淨係受衫顏色影響<br />\nNet gain=rx-ry<br />\n<br />\nCase 1(black):<br />\n吸散快所以r&gt;1<br />\nSo rx&gt;ry<br />\nSo net gain正數<br />\n<br />\nCase 2(white)<br />\n掉轉所以r&lt;1<br />\nSo rx&lt;ry<br />\nNet gain變負數&mdash;&gt;散熱<br />\n<br />\n當然受其他因素影響<br />\n但neglect所有野consider only colour<br />\n白色係散熱快 所以著淺色係common sense"},{"pid":"c2fea75e520c2cfcf9846ffd91036419715838b1","tid":784551,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caa9a9fe0abe931776551a67b24564d6f52128f6","tid":784551,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:02:42.000Z","msg":"話說喺早排陽光猛烈嘅日子小弟著咗套全黑嘅運動衫褲踩單車，但就俾班friend笑鳩我著深色衫吸熱（佢地都係著淺色衫）。<br />\n<br />\n小弟我得中三嘅物理程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係知黑色係良好嘅輻射吸收體，雖然吸熱勁咗，但理論上散熱都快咗，既然身體溫度高過戶外溫度，咁散熱效能應該高啲？<br />\n<br />\n而我班friend就認為淺色衫可以反射返啲陽光同輻射，令到身體冇咁熱。<br />\n<br />\n咁我諗呢條問題應該涉及究竟散熱同吸熱邊樣快啲，但奈何我唔識物理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁假設喺室外氣溫係33&deg;c ，人體氣溫38&deg;c，並且喺陽光直接照射下運動，究竟運動嗰陣應該著淺色定深色衫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能條問題對你地嚟講好戇鳩，但我未學過真係唔識，屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:49:55.000Z","msg":"樓主呢排個心點?有冇update?"},{"pid":"69dd4e6d574c214b250ea85428f4dd775e951fa3","tid":784551,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2fea75e520c2cfcf9846ffd91036419715838b1","tid":784551,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caa9a9fe0abe931776551a67b24564d6f52128f6","tid":784551,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:02:42.000Z","msg":"話說喺早排陽光猛烈嘅日子小弟著咗套全黑嘅運動衫褲踩單車，但就俾班friend笑鳩我著深色衫吸熱（佢地都係著淺色衫）。<br />\n<br />\n小弟我得中三嘅物